AI-FANN
=======

This module provides a Perl wrapper for the FANN library
(http://fann.sf.net).

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the FANN library version 2.0.0 or later compiled
to use doubles internally.

The module Test::More is also required for testing.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

You may need to add extra parameters to the Makefile.PL script to
indicate where to find the FANN library and include files if they are
not installed on some standard locations (i.e. /usr/lib or
/usr/local/lib).

Read ExtUtils::MakeMaker documentation for intructions about how to do
it.


